OL,3,COne in five pro footballers using snus
OL,4,Cor nicotine pouches, survey finds
OL,6,FA new study has revealed that around
OL,7,Fone in five professional footballers
OL,8,Fuse snus or nicotine pouches, ITV
OL,9,FNews' Cari Davies has more
OL,11,FAround one in five male and female
OL,12,Fprofessional players who took part in
OL,13,Fa new survey are currently using snus,
OL,14,Fnicotine pouches or both.
OL,16,FThe study by Loughborough University,
OL,17,Fcommissioned by the Professional
OL,18,FFootballers' Association (PFA), also
OL,19,Fidentified that two out of five had
OL,20,Ftried the pouches at least once in the
OL,21,Fpast.
