OL,3,COne in five pro footballers using snus
OL,4,Cor nicotine pouches, survey finds
OL,6,FSnus contains tobacco and is not
OL,7,Flegally available to buy in the UK.
OL,9,FTobacco-free nicotine pouches are
OL,10,Flegal to buy, and were found to be
OL,11,Fmore commonly used among players. The
OL,12,Fpouches are usually placed between the
OL,13,Fupper lip and the gums.
OL,15,FThe report states the true figures are
OL,16,F"likely" to be even higher due to
OL,17,Fplayers not wanting to disclose use,
OL,18,Feven in an anonymous survey.
