OL,3,COne in five pro footballers using snus
OL,4,Cor nicotine pouches, survey finds
OL,6,FAround 18% of the 628 male players
OL,7,Fsurveyed, based at either Premier
OL,8,FLeague or EFL clubs, said they
OL,9,Fcurrently used it.
OL,11,FOf the 51 Women's Super League players
OL,12,Fsurveyed, 22% said used snus.
OL,14,FParticipants said improved mental
OL,15,Freadiness was a key benefit of the
OL,16,Fsubstance, with 41% of male players
OL,17,Fsaying they used it to help relax,
OL,18,Fmost commonly after training and after
OL,19,Fmatches. That figure was 64% among
OL,20,Ffemale players.
