OL,3,COne in five pro footballers using snus
OL,4,Cor nicotine pouches, survey finds
OL,6,FOne of the 16 professional club
OL,7,Fperformance and medical staff members
OL,8,Falso interviewed for the report said
OL,9,Fplayers used it as a "coping
OL,10,Fmechanism".
OL,12,FThe pouches are also used as an
OL,13,Fappetite suppressant, the report found.
OL,15,FHowever, the report also highlighted
OL,16,Fthe potential negative physical
OL,17,Fimpacts.
