OL,3,COne in five pro footballers using snus
OL,4,Cor nicotine pouches, survey finds
OL,6,FEvidence suggests snus is associated
OL,7,Fwith an increased risk of oesophagus
OL,8,Fand pancreatic cancer in comparison to
OL,9,Fnon-smokers, and to an increased risk
OL,10,Fof cardiovascular disease.
OL,12,FThere is strong evidence of an
OL,13,Fassociation between snus use and mouth
OL,14,Flesions.
OL,16,FThe survey found users often started
OL,17,Fusing the products in a bid to fit in
OL,18,Fwith other, often more senior, team-
OL,19,Fmates. For male players 56% gave this
OL,20,Fas a reason, rising to 73% among women.
