OL,3,COne in five pro footballers using snus
OL,4,Cor nicotine pouches, survey finds
OL,6,FOne surveyed player admitted: "I have
OL,7,Fquit twice for eight months but always
OL,8,Fseem to start doing it again. I find
OL,9,Fit hard to quit when I'm around it all
OL,10,Fday."
OL,12,FA staff member at a club said they had
OL,13,Fcome across a player whose career had
OL,14,Fmainly been spent in the Premier
OL,15,FLeague and Championship who described
OL,16,Fthemselves as a "heavy user".
