OL,3,COne in five pro footballers using snus
OL,4,Cor nicotine pouches, survey finds
OL,6,FThey told the staff member: "I'd love
OL,7,Fto come off it, but I can't. It's just
OL,8,Feverywhere I look. Every other
OL,9,Fplayer's taking it, I go to fill my
OL,10,Fcar up and it's at the pump stands.
OL,11,FIt's just too easy."
OL,13,FApproximately half the current users
OL,14,Fin the men's game said they wanted to
OL,15,Fquit within the next 12 months.
OL,17,FUsers also reported suffering from
OL,18,Fnicotine dependence, such as using it
OL,19,Fwithout awareness or intention.
